OL,7,FAs councils increase their tax so too
OL,8,Fdoes the amount of bailiffs they hire,
OL,9,FITV News Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FIt's the knock on the door everyone
OL,13,Fstruggling to pay council tax fears
OL,14,Fmost.
OL,16,FJess King is one of those who heard
OL,17,Fthat knock. In Yorkshire, where she
OL,18,Flives, as in most places across
OL,19,FEngland and Wales, council tax has
OL,20,Fgone up by as much as is allowed.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/15
