OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FWhen Jess fell behind on paying her
OL,8,Fbills she was grieving after the death
OL,9,Fof her newborn baby and still looking
OL,10,Fafter her other children.
OL,12,FJess told ITV News: "I had a bailiff
OL,13,Fturn up at my house, and I had my
OL,14,Flittle girl with me at the time. I got
OL,15,Fvery upset; I was crying.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
