OL,3,CCouncils referred 600,000 people to
OL,4,Cbailiffs last year - as tax arrears
OL,5,Crise
OL,7,F"My daughter was so scared - she was
OL,8,Fclinging to me; hiding behind my legs.
OL,9,FShe was asking who the bad man was
OL,10,Fbecause it's very intimidating; they
OL,11,Fhave quite an aggressive tone. Stood
OL,12,Fin my doorway; wouldn't leave."
OL,14,FJess isn't alone.
OL,16,FITV News sent Freedom of Information
OL,17,Frequests to around 100 of the biggest
OL,18,Fcouncils in England.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/15
