OL,3,CCouncils referred 600,000 people to
OL,4,Cbailiffs last year - as tax arrears
OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FThe responses we had revealed that the
OL,8,Ftotal amount owed in council tax
OL,9,Farrears has increased by over 70% in
OL,10,Fthe past 5 years.
OL,12,FThe councils that responded to our
OL,13,Finformation request told us that last
OL,14,Fyear alone over one million people
OL,15,Fhave received a court summons because
OL,16,Fthey are in council tax arrears.
OL,18,FAnd almost 600,000 people have been
OL,19,Freferred to bailiffs - that's an
OL,20,Faverage of one referral every minute.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/15
