OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FThe Noah's Ark Centre is a charity in
OL,8,FHalifax which offers free debt advice
OL,9,Fto local people.
OL,11,FAndrew Sykes, one of the charity's
OL,12,Ffounders, is worried that as council
OL,13,Ftax bills - and arrears - increase, so
OL,14,Fwill the number of referrals to
OL,15,Fbailiffs. He is calling for local
OL,16,Fauthorities to stop using bailiffs to
OL,17,Frecover council tax debt.
OL,19,FMr Sykes says: "For too long, they've
OL,20,Fdefaulted to this 'cheap option' of
OL,21,Fusing enforcement agents.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
