OL,5,Crise
OL,7,F"The reason it's cheap is because they
OL,8,Fdon't charge the local authority
OL,9,Fanything for their instruction. They
OL,10,Fmake their fees on the back of the
OL,11,Fclients that are paying the debt.
OL,12,FTheir fees get added onto the debt."
OL,14,FIn North London, ITV News went out
OL,15,Fwith volunteers who are part of
OL,16,Fanother campaign to reduce the use of
OL,17,Fbailiffs by local authorities
OL,18,Fcollecting council tax.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/15
