OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FSome councils - including Bristol,
OL,8,FManchester and Hammersmith and Fulham
OL,9,F- have already made changes.
OL,11,FCampaigner Maddie Ryan Tucker says:
OL,12,F"We think it's a harmful practice.
OL,13,FPeople are in debt, they're
OL,14,Fstruggling. They need help, they need
OL,15,Fassistance, but instead they're
OL,16,Fgetting letters saying bailiffs are
OL,17,Fbeing sent to the house, which is
OL,18,Fthreatening.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/15
