OL,7,F"And then when the bailiffs do turn
OL,8,Fup, they're aggressive, they're rude,
OL,9,Fthey're hostile".
OL,11,FThe Local Government Association told
OL,12,FITV News in a statment: "Enforcement
OL,13,Fagents should only ever be used as a
OL,14,Flast resort.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/15
