OL,5,Crise
OL,7,F"Before the situation reaches a stage
OL,8,Fwhere enforcement agents are involved,
OL,9,Fseveral letters should have been
OL,10,Fwritten, people should have been
OL,11,Fencouraged to apply for financial
OL,12,Fsupport, and efforts should be made to
OL,13,Farrange new payment plans."
OL,15,FSupport with council tax is available
OL,16,Ffor those who are eligible, but at the
OL,17,Fmoment an estimated #2.9 billion of
OL,18,Fthat help is going unclaimed.
