OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FMichelle Neal hadn't realised she
OL,8,Fqualified for council tax reductions
OL,9,Fwhen she fell behind and bailiffs'
OL,10,Fletters started to arrive. Now, she's
OL,11,Fworking to get the information - and
OL,12,Fthe money - to others.
OL,14,FMs Neal says: "I just didn't know what
OL,15,Fto do. You can go on a list that's
OL,16,Fknown as being a vulnerable customer.
OL,17,FSome people don't even know about that.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/15
