OL,5,Crise
OL,7,F"They have a little bit more of
OL,8,Fspecialist team, that can help you out
OL,9,Fwith that. But I didn't know about any
OL,10,Fof this until this last year. I think
OL,11,Fcouncils should be giving that
OL,12,Finformation out".
OL,14,FChris Lucas-Jones is a bailiff with 20
OL,15,Fyears' experience. He agreed to speak
OL,16,Fto ITV News to tell a side of the
OL,17,Fstory he says is rarely reported.
