OL,7,FHe says: "You get so many people that
OL,8,Flie to bailiffs and say that they are
OL,9,Fa vulnerable person, they can't pay.
OL,10,FAnd then when you get down to their
OL,11,Fproperty, you see there's a different
OL,12,Fside to it.
OL,14,F"Yes, the agents do get paid
OL,15,Fincentives, but those incentives -
OL,16,Fthey also do get paid for being fair
OL,17,Fwith that individual".
